  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large pot over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until caramelized, stirring occasionally.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the panang paste and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the tomato paste and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the diced tomatoes, dried white beans, and water to the pot.",
    "Bring the mixture to a boil, then reduce the heat to low and simmer for 1 hour.",
    "Stir in the balsamic vinegar and season with salt and pepper to taste.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with fresh parsley or dill."
